<|channel>thought
<channel|># 從頭再嚟
(pos:動詞/成語)
<explanation>
yue:重新開始，由最初嘅階段再做過一次
eng:to start all over again / to start from scratch
<eg>
yue:既然件事搞砸咗，不如我哋就從頭再嚟啦。 (zeon3 gin3 si6 gin6 gaau2 zaat6 zo2, bat1 jyu4 ngo5 dei6 zau6 cung4 tau4 zoi3 lai4 laa1.)
eng:Since things have gone wrong, why don't we just start all over again. [end of text]


